#### 6. No Assertion — `ApplyBulkDiscount_Works` (line 68–74)

A 10% discount is applied but the resulting prices are never checked. A math bug (e.g., `Price * fraction` instead of `Price * (1 - fraction)`) passes silently.

**Fix:**
```csharp
[TestMethod]
public void ApplyBulkDiscount_ReducesPricesByFraction()
{
    _catalog.AddProduct(new Product("SKU-001", "Widget", 100.00m));
    _catalog.ApplyBulkDiscount(0.10m);

    Assert.AreEqual(90.00m, _catalog.GetProduct("SKU-001")!.Price);
}
```

